info.description:
# about
this a simple package which is take only DataFrame or numpy array and give the output StandardScaler

## installation
'''pip install mystd'''

##Modules
there is one modules in the package 'mystd'.
In mystd module there is two function.
1. std
2. myshape

## How to use it?
Open terminl

type 

'''mystd.std(df)'''

This is take pandas DataFrame or Numpy array and return the StandardScaler

'''mystd.myshape(df)'''

this is take a pandas dataFrame or numpy array and return the shape
